{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Create an independent Safeguarding Body.",
        "additional_details": "Without this body, we feel vulnerable adults have no higher authority to ensure safety.\r\n \r\nWe believe the system forces agencies to investigate themselves, creating conflicts of interest and leaving people unprotected. We think no effective independent body exists to oversee or intervene when local authorities fail to safeguard the vulnerable.\r\n",
        "background": "We urge the creation of an independent safeguarding body to:\r\n \r\nInvestigate institutional abuse objectively.\r\nReview local authority decisions\r\nProtect vulnerable adults effectively.\r\n",
